-- Vale, Striking Nickel Workers in Ontario Begin Third Day of Labor Talks
-- Christopher Donville
-- 2010-06-21T13:05:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/vale-striking-nickel-workers-in-ontario-begin-third-day-of-labor-talks.html

          
          
             Vale SA and about 3,000 striking
nickel workers in Sudbury and Port Colborne, Ontario, will
resume contract negotiations for a third day, a company
spokesman said.  
 “The talks are continuing today,” Cory McPhee said in a
telephone interview from Sudbury.  
